name: OS Tycoon Wiki
tagline: A private development log for OS Tycoon, being developed by Plethora Studios.
body:
Hello, I am apljee, or Austin! I am from Plethora Studios.

At Plethora Studios, we have recently announced our brand-new title: OS Tycoon! We are actively working on it and have already managed to create the main menu in under one day. We are actively looking for staff also, so if you, or someone else you know, has experience in JavaScript or HTML5, please, contact us on the greenheart games forums.

forum.greenheartgames.com

My username: apljee
Cody's username: Killertoad
Liam's username: Resinex112


Austin
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
